建议技能判定标准和结果：(不含 pfm 消耗)
** 仅有判定条件/效果建议值，其它维持原有设定。
** 针对原著中比较强的功夫可适当放宽判定/效果。

my_level = 玩家人物等级(1-50)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+ 暗器
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
命中条件： random(valid_throw_level + my_level) > (your_valid_dodge_level)/2
A 命中伤害：dam = random(valid_throw_level) + weapon_dam * (2 + random(4))
  自己：busy(2+random(2))
B 不命中：自己 busy(4+random(3))
发现来源判断： your_dex > random(my_dex)+10

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+ busy
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
命中条件： random(valid_skill_level + my_level) > 
		(your_valid_dodge_level + your_valid_parry_level)/4
A 命中： busy = 2 + sqrt( this_skill_level/10 )
B 不命中： 自己busy(2+random(4))

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+ 一招晕
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
命中条件： random(valid_skill_level + mylevel)/2 + 20 > 
		(your_valid_dodge_level)/2
A 命中： unconcious()
B 不命中，尝试普通攻击： random(valid_skill_level + mylevel) > (your_valid_dodge_level)/2
  B.A 这次命中，dam_qi = random(this_skill_level)
      自己：自己busy(2+random(2))
  B.B 再次失败: 自己busy(4+random(4))